<c74object name='sp.corpusanalysis' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>Analyze all the samples in a folder</digest>
    <description>Analyze all the samples in a folder to create a corpus.</description>
    <discussion>    <h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
    <p>The <o>sp.corpusanalysis</o> object works in conjunction with <o>sp.folderloop</o> to analyze all the samples in a folder for a variety of descriptors, timeframes, and metadata to be used in <o>sp.corpusmatch</o>. Keeps track of the location of the samples when analyzed.</p>
</discussion>

	<metadatalist>
		<metadata name='author'>Rodrigo Constanzo, Flucoma Project</metadata>
		<metadata name='tag'>Machine Learning</metadata>
		<metadata name='tag'>Drums</metadata>
	</metadatalist>

